{"tid":392904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇原居民覺得班生蕃移民扮local好好笑","createTime":"2017-09-08T22:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T00:57:36.000Z","uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07323abfca4fc17b3d1c45d417789349249451ef","tid":392904,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T22:25:03.000Z","msg":"移民黎香港 仲要嚮度圍內鬥<br />\n成班都係走難黎既蝗 分別只係新蝗同舊蝗<br />\n屌政府偏袒原居民喎 你地憑乜黎攤分利益<br />\n鵲巢鳩佔 60-90年代係有機遇<br />\n唔係你班移民貢獻 走啦你地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6e04c92e67710a9ac8cf2bbcec47c60073bbec","tid":392904,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T22:40:06.000Z","msg":"移民負評但唔敢回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n走啦你地 唔好再攪香港<br />\n想搶我地應得丁權 又話新界人黑社會<br />\n就算係又點 你唔係呢度人 入鄉隨俗啦<br />\n唔係你父母個代游水黎 再嚮香港出世就叫香港人<br />\n頂多係中國難民或移民後裔"},{"pid":"fab15a6f67e32e962df41c4029ab76887c8eb20e","tid":392904,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T22:52:17.000Z","msg":"走啦你地 呢個地方係有原居民"},{"pid":"c3ae1742001bbb95786b228e0042a1ca9a64c996","tid":392904,"uid":138553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"真野唔好講出來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輕輕一推"}]}